\/12\/31\/son-of-adam-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36255,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: I will forgive you without reservation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 31, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah Almighty said: O son of Adam, if you call upon Me and place your hope in Me, I will forgive you despite what is within you and I will not hesitate. O son of Adam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38341,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/09\/qadr-happiness\/","url_meta":{"origin":36255,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Happiness in being pleased with Allah\u2019s decrees","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 9, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAmong the happiness of the son of Adam is to be satisfied with what Allah has decreed for him. Among the misery of the son of Adam is to abandon asking Allah for guidance, and among the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35889,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/use-free-time-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":36255,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on \u2018Ibadah: Use free time to worship Allah, enrich the heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019qil ibn Yasar rep